##future# Binance Futures Trading Bot

Python trading bot for Binance Futures Testnet.

## Features
- Market Orders
- Limit Orders
- BUY and SELL support
- Logging
- Input Validation

## Run

pip install -r requirements.txt

python cli.py --symbol BTCUSDT --side BUY --order_type MARKET --quantity 0.001
